<div class="min-h-screen bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <div class="bg-white shadow rounded-lg p-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
        <div>
          <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">안녕하세요, <%= @user.display_name %>님!</h1>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium
              <%= @user.admin? ? 'bg-red-100 text-red-800' : @user.teacher? ? 'bg-green-100 text-green-800' : 'bg-blue-100 text-blue-800' %>">
              <%= @user.role_i18n %>
            </span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <%= button_to "로그아웃", destroy_user_session_path,
              method: :delete,
              class: "inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm font-medium text-gray-700 bg-white hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-4">대시보드</h2>

        <% if @user.student? %>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-blue-900">질문 생성 연습</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-blue-700">새로운 콘텐츠로 질문 만들기를 연습하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-green-900">내 기록</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-green-700">지금까지 작성한 질문과 피드백을 확인하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-900">성장 리포트</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-purple-700">나의 발문 능력 성장 과정을 확인하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% elsif @user.teacher? %>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
            <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-blue-900">콘텐츠 관리</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-blue-700">학습 자료를 등록하고 관리하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-green-900">학생 관리</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-green-700">학생들의 학습 현황을 확인하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-purple-900">리포트</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-purple-700">학급 전체의 학습 분석 리포트를 확인하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% else %>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="bg-red-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-red-900">사용자 관리</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-red-700">전체 사용자를 관리하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-yellow-50 rounded-lg p-6">
              <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-yellow-900">시스템 설정</h3>
              <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-yellow-700">시스템 전체 설정을 관리하세요.</p>
              <div class="mt-4">
                <span class="text-gray-400 text-sm">(준비 중)</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
